      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What are the best Q without U words in Scrabble?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "The essential Q-without-U words are: QI (11 points), QOPH (18 points), QADI (14 points), QAID (14 points), QANAT (14 points), QINTAR (15 points), QWERTY (21 points, SOWPODS only), and TRANQ (14 points). QI alone solves most Q-without-U situations since it only needs an I." }
      },
