        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How do the odds of drawing Q change as the game progresses?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "If Q hasn't been drawn, the probability increases as the bag shrinks. With 60 tiles remaining, your chance rises to about 11.7%. With 40 tiles remaining, it's about 17.5%. With 20 tiles left, it jumps to 35%. Tile tracking lets you prepare by holding U or learning Q-without-U words." }
      }
    ]
  })} />

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <article class="prose prose-invert prose-gray max-w-none">
      <nav class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6 not-prose flex items-center gap-1">
        <a href="/blog/" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">← Blog</a>
        <span class="mx-1">›</span>
        <span class="text-gray-300">Statistics</span>
