        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">QI solves <span class="text-white font-medium">90% of Q-without-U situations</span>. It only needs an I (9 tiles in the bag). On a Triple Letter Score, QI scores 22 points. Even a basic QI play gives you 11 points and dumps the Q immediately.</p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">When to Exchange Q</h2>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/10">
