        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">🎯 Summary</p>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">You'll draw Q in your opening hand about <span class="text-white font-medium">7% of games (1 in 14)</span>. As the bag shrinks, the probability rises — reaching 35% with 20 tiles left. Always have a plan: know QI and at least 3-4 other Q-without-U words. Exchange Q early if you can't play it within 1-2 turns. Never get stuck with Q at game end.</p>
